Q7. Calculate the factorial of a number using lambda function.

Solution :-

def factorial(n):
    if n == 0:
        return 1
    else:
        return n * factorial(n - 1)

n = int(input("Enter a number: "))
lambda_fun = lambda n: 1 if n == 0 else n * factorial(n - 1)

ans = lambda_fun(n)

print(f"The factorial of {n} is: {ans}")
